Step 1: Turn on 8086 Trainer Kit
Step 2: Enter Assembler using A
Step 3: Enter Program Starting From Address 1000H

For Anticlockwise Rotation:-
Step 4: Enter Values 0A, 06, 05, 09 at memory locations 2000H - 2003H using SB
Step 5: Execute Program using GO 1000
Step 6: Verify Rotation of Stepper Motor

For Cockwise Rotation:-
Step 4: Enter Values 09, 05, 06, 0A at memory locations 2000H - 2003H using SB
Step 5: Execute Program using GO 1000
Step 6: Verify Rotation of Stepper Motor